    dc:description "FIGURE 33. E. ophisauri. Gravid: A—head end, lateral view; B—anterior part of body, lateral view; C—tail end, lateral view. Subgravid: D—head end, lateral view; E—vulva and proximal part of anterior syngonium, lateral view; F—bend of posterior genital tube with oviduct; G—tail, lateral view. Scale bars: A, C...G—0.1 mm; B—0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5262697/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

